Visualizar series

gei <- read_delim(here("datos", "emisiones-gei-por-sector_dncc.csv"),
                  delim = ";") 
## 
##  Column specification 
## cols(
##   emisiones_gei_anio = col_double(),
##   emisiones_gei_sector = col_character(),
##   emisiones_gei = col_double(),
##   `emisiones_gei_unidad_medida,,` = col_character()
## )
colnames(gei) <- c("anio", "sector", "emisiones", "unidad_medida")

gei <- gei %>% 
  mutate(unidad_medida = str_remove(unidad_medida, ",,"),
         sector = if_else(sector == "energia", "Energa", sector))

write_csv(gei, here("datos", "emisiones_gei.csv"))
gei %>% 
  filter(sector == "Energa") %>% 
  ggplot(aes(anio, emisiones)) +
  geom_point() 

gei %>% 
  filter(sector == "Energa") %>% 
  ggplot(aes(anio, emisiones)) +
  geom_line()

gei %>% 
  filter(sector == "Energa") %>% 
  ggplot(aes(anio, emisiones)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_line()

gei %>% 
  filter(anio %in% c(2002, 2003, 2005, 2007)) %>% 
  filter(sector == "Energa") %>% 
  ggplot(aes(anio, emisiones)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_line()

gei %>% 
  ggplot(aes(anio, emisiones)) +
  geom_point(aes(color = sector, shape = sector),
             size = 2) +
  geom_line(aes(color = sector)) +
  # scale_color_brewer(palette = "Dark2") +
  scale_x_continuous(expand = c(0.01, 0.01)) +
  guides(color = guide_legend(nrow = 2)) +
  labs(x = "Ao", y = latex2exp::TeX("Emision (Mt CO_2eq)"),
       color = NULL, shape = NULL) +
  theme_minimal(base_size = 14) +
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")
